ntopng: ntopng (next generation network top)
ntopng:
ntopng: ntopng is a tool for both Unix and Win32 that shows the network 
ntopng: usage, similar to what the popular top Unix command does. 
ntopng: It sports a web interface for accessing accounting data and includes
ntopng: support for popular tools/protocols as well DPI and host categorisation.
